==English==

===Noun===
{{wikipedia|Anti-homosexualism}}

{{en-noun|-}}

1 is the fight against and active disagreement to homosexual practices, beliefs and attitudes but not against individuals that link to       them.  (christian position)

2 is the [[political]] targeting of [[homosexual|homosexuals]] for attack or opposition by a political or [[religious]] group.

